room_title: Escape room "The Untouchables" by Exit Strategy Escape Room in Cumberland
room_description: Welcome to the untouchables. Eliot Ness has hired you to help him bring down the biggest gangster of them all - the infamous Al Capone! We have a warrant to search one of his private speakeasies and we have reason to believe his ledger is hidden in there somewhere. You have exactly one hour to either swim with the fishes or find it and put him away for good!
